high_descs: go  the end of the island
pick up the spoon from the counter top
take the spoon to the stove
stand the spoon up on it's end in the pan on the stove
pick up the pan from the stove
take the pan with the spoon to the sink
put the pan and spoon in the sink
anns.task_desc: put a spoon in a pan and take them to the sink

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the side of the silver island counter to the right.
Pick up the spoon to the left of the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the white stove.
Put the spoon into the pan in the back left corner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the spoon from the stove.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the pan with the spoon inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a spoon in a sink.

high_descs: Take a step to the left to face the end of the table in the center of the kitchen.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the center table in the kitchen.
Turn right and step forward to face the stove.
Place the knife in the pan on the back left burner.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it on the stove.
Turn to the right and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the pan with a knife in it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife in a pan as well as move them to the sink.
